cast.overview: Mumbai, India, November 26, 2008. While several terrorists spread hatred and death through the city, others attack the Taj Mahal Palace Hotel. Both hotel staff and guests risk their lives, making unthinkable sacrifices to protect themselves and keep everyone safe while help arrives.
cast.title: Hotel Mumbai

details.biography: Angus McLaren (born 3 November 1988) is an Australian actor and musician. He is best known for his roles in the television series Packed to the Rafters as Nathan Rafter.  He made his professional debut when he was 12 years old with a recurring role on the ABC series Something in the Air.
details.name: Angus McLaren
